	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />To answer your question, there is no hardware functionality to stretch the screen horizontally. But that doesn't mean you can't have a horizontal stretching effect, it will just require using pattern and or nametable manipulation to achieve the effect.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


